I've decided to evacuate to the shelter
with my nan.

rows.label: tlk70000011_05_msg0002

I'll probably have to let go of the shop,
but nan said I'm more important to her
than this place. Made it easier.

rows.label: tlk70000011_05_msg0003

So... Do you want to buy any of my
leftover stock?
